abstract: Michelle Higgins reviews Pennings Farm Market Pub & Grill in Warwick, NY (Metropolitan/New Jersey).
lead_paragraph: Pennings Farm Market Pub & Grill in Warwick, N.Y., just over the New Jersey state line in Orange County, has groceries and garden supplies in one corner, craft beers and comfort food at the other.
